# --- PureIce Nitrogen ---
lbn r0 SORTER PINitrogen ReferenceId Maximum
lbn r2 SILO_TYPE PINitrogen Quantity 3
slt r4 r2 SILO_MAX
sll r1 ICON_PINitrogen 8
or r1 r1 OP
