# --- PureIce Hydrazine ---
lbn r0 SORTER PIHydrazine ReferenceId Maximum
lbn r2 SILO_TYPE PIHydrazine Quantity 3
slt r4 r2 SILO_MAX
sll r1 ICON_PIHydrazine 8
